{"type": "article", "id": 24739, "title": "轻便型扳手", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-31T06:52:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 171, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702153221I3HjkPXaucbFmCEW.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是台湾设计团队 Mininch 新推出的一个扳手，它的外形像一把尺子或者刀片。工具里面可以放 5 个可替换的拱形模块，上面有不同大小的六角形空缺或者其他形状的空缺来拧螺丝，以替代原本非常笨重的扳手，也方便携带。它一共有 10 种模块替换，目前正在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/2054052511/wrenchit-turning-smart\">这里是众筹链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153216HMKj1oCidtysUgnA.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.6247619\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153217b8Ejm6McxA0k2W9w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52380952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153217lrqK6LCnyiSMsu89.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52380952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153218l9pMdBGALuSJWi6r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52380952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153219lkSLuOytMg5UQP8p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153219tqF276zYwvfmPipo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}